1. *Ruku* mi je držao čvrsto. (He held my hand firmly.)
2. Čvrsto mi je stisnuo *ruku*. (He firmly shook my hand.)
3. Okrenuo je *ruku* i pogledao sat. (He turned his hand and looked at the watch.)
4. Poželela sam da mu stisnem *ruku*. (I wanted to shake his hand.)
5. Spustio je *ruku* na moju ruku. (He put his hand on my hand.)
6. Uspeo je da uhvati *ruku*. (He managed to catch his hand.)